               <p>For the Prosecution, <rs id="t18191201-157-viclabel898" type="occupation">MESSRS.</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-157-victim1566 t18191201-157-viclabel898"></join>
